retrogametech I installed CR2032 my Pokemon silver cartridge I considered battery holder again I wasnt really satisfied I had keep using small battery I just guessed larger battery would keep my save file longer I mean same voltage twice size thus much bigger capacity If original battery kept my save file about 11 years new one should hit 1520 years mark quite easily.What I did cut old battery from its metal pins simple placed new larger battery those pins I didnt use solder cartridge case alone when closed aplied enough pressure keep place I did use one small strip electric tape keep larger battery contacts away from cartridge PCB though As I said before its tight fit cartridge kinda get little bulkier where new battery about 1mm doesnt do any damage cartridge case gameboy It still slides easily any Gameboy related product without ploblems its been working fine until now Ive done mod about 2 years ago "
